headline: 3 Growth Stocks That Beat the S&P 500 in 2024 but Are Still Worth Buying in 2025
summary: Beating the S&P 500 in 2024 was no easy task, even for growth stocks.  Here's why all three growth stocks are still worth buying in 2025.  Scott Levine (Archer Aviation): In addition to positive analyst coverage and the formation of a new partnership in the Middle East, a variety of factors provided a lift for Archer Aviation stock, helping it to soar nearly 59% higher in 2024.
